sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor StoreManager
participant InventoryConsole
participant InventoryService
participant Utils
participant InventoryRepository
participant InventoryJson as inventory.json

== Add Product ==
StoreManager->>InventoryConsole: Select "Add Product"
InventoryConsole->>StoreManager: Prompt for name and quantity
StoreManager-->>InventoryConsole: name, quantity
InventoryConsole->>InventoryService: addProduct(name, quantity)
InventoryService->>Utils: isNonEmptyText(name)
InventoryService->>Utils: isNonNegativeQuantity(quantity)
alt valid product data
  InventoryService->>InventoryService: generateNextProductId()
  InventoryService->>InventoryService: append Product
  InventoryService-->>InventoryConsole: created Product
  InventoryConsole->>InventoryService: getAllProducts()
  InventoryService-->>InventoryConsole: products
  InventoryConsole->>InventoryRepository: saveProducts(products)
  InventoryRepository->>InventoryJson: write updated products array
  InventoryJson-->>InventoryRepository: persisted
  InventoryRepository-->>InventoryConsole: save complete
  InventoryConsole-->>StoreManager: Display success and product ID
else invalid name or negative quantity
  InventoryService-->>InventoryConsole: validation failure
  InventoryConsole-->>StoreManager: Display error message
end
